  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PERU/Life W Conservation a Ecological Restoration of Atiquipa</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims for the conservation, restoration and sustainable use of the Atiquipa Lomas. The project emcompasses following components: 1) biodiversity conservation, 2) water resources management and 3) climate change adaptation. Overall Objective is to conserve and recover native lomas forest in Atiquipa and ensure its conservation through active participation of local actors. The project aims to improve the capacity of the lomas to sustain livelihoods through strengthened organizational capacities at the local level for sustainable management of natural resources and adaptation to climate change.</narrative>
  </description>
